                               	                                <b> Beware of Phishing Attacks: </b><br><br>
                                       	                        </font>

                                               	                <font face="Cambria" size="3" color="black">

                                                       	        <b>-</b> Do not give your <b>LDAP USERID & PASSWORD</b> to anyone.<br>
                                                               	<b>-</b> Do not enter LDAP login information in any pop up window.<br>
	                                                        <b>-</b> Do not reply to any mail asking your login information for any<br>
        	                                                         reason.<br>
                	                                        <b>-</b> Do not enter your LDAP login information on any unknown website.<br>
                        	                                <b>-</b> Phishing is  a  fraudulent attempt,  usually made  through email seeking <br>
                               	                                your userid, password and personal information.<br>
                                       	                        <b>-</b> Please report  immediately  on  <b>help@cc.iitb.ac.in</b>  if you receive any<br>
	                                               	                 such email.<br>
                                                       	        <b>-</b> Immediately change your passwords if you have accidentally revealed <br>
                                                                	your credentials.<br>
	                                                        <b>- Computer Center never asks you for such information.</b><br>
       	                                                        </font>
